OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772824283
OL,3,CVeteran's widow in appeal to MOD to
OL,4,Callow bereavement payment
OL,6,FA veteran's widow from Enniskillen has
OL,7,Fmade an emotional appeal to the
OL,8,FMinistry of Defence to drop a
OL,9,Fchallenge to a bereavement payment for
OL,10,Fher family.
OL,12,FJonny Cole suffered from Post
OL,13,FTraumatic Stress Disorder following
OL,14,Ftwo tours of Afghanistan but wasn't
OL,15,Fdiagnosed until after he died by
OL,16,Fsuicide.
OL,18,FHis wife Teresa has told UTV the
OL,19,Fappeal against compensation for her
OL,20,Ffamily is adding to their trauma.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772824283
OL,3,CVeteran's widow in appeal to MOD to
OL,4,Callow bereavement payment
OL,6,F"How much more do you want me to
OL,7,Fendure the pain and suffering and the
OL,8,Ftrauma that I have had to go through?"
OL,9,Fshe said.
OL,11,FJonny Cole served in the Army for over
OL,12,F17 years. He was injured in a Taliban
OL,13,Frocket attack and left tormented by
OL,14,Fthe horrors he experienced on the
OL,15,Fbattlefields of Afghanistan.
OL,17,FJonny died by suicide in 2018.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772824283
OL,3,CVeteran's widow in appeal to MOD to
OL,4,Callow bereavement payment
OL,6,FHe was suffering post-traumatic stress
OL,7,Fdisorder, but that was only diagnosed
OL,8,Fafter his death. A coroner found he
OL,9,Fhad been failed by the NHS and
OL,10,FMinistry of Defence.
OL,12,F"I would like to think that if my
OL,13,Fhusband had been cared for, looked
OL,14,Fafter by, as he called it 'his
OL,15,Ffamily', the Army, that he would still
OL,16,Fbe alive today," said Theresa.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772824283
OL,3,CVeteran's widow in appeal to MOD to
OL,4,Callow bereavement payment
OL,6,FA Belfast court ruled Teresa is
OL,7,Feligible for what's called a
OL,8,Fbereavement claim - compensation
OL,9,Fawarded to families of service
OL,10,Fpersonnel who died due to MOD
OL,11,Fnegligence.
OL,13,FHowever the payment was stopped before
OL,14,Fit even began as the MOD is
OL,15,Fchallenging the decision.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
