OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772824283
OL,3,CVeteran's widow in appeal to MOD to
OL,4,Callow bereavement payment
OL,6,FTheresa said: "It has come as a
OL,7,Fbombshell, and I've been left robbing
OL,8,FPeter to pay Paul. I've had total
OL,9,Fbreakdown in my life - I never thought
OL,10,FI would suffer as bad with my mental
OL,11,Fhealth as what I have."
OL,13,FIn a statement, an MOD spokesperson
OL,14,Fsaid: "Any death by suicide is a
OL,15,Ftragedy that is felt across our
OL,16,Fcommunity, and our thoughts are with
OL,17,FJonny's loved ones.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/7
