PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772824283
OL,3,CVeteran's widow in appeal to MOD to
OL,4,Callow bereavement payment
OL,6,F"We are committed to renewing the
OL,7,Fcontract with those who serve, have
OL,8,Fserved, and their families and are
OL,9,Fdetermined to provide those
OL,10,Fexperiencing metal health challenges
OL,11,Fwith the support they need.
OL,13,F"More than #25 million has been
OL,14,Finvested into Op COURAGE in 2025/26,
OL,15,Fso that veterans in England can
OL,16,Fcontinue to access specialist NHS
OL,17,Fmental health and wellbeing services.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/7
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1772824283
OL,3,CVeteran's widow in appeal to MOD to
OL,4,Callow bereavement payment
OL,6,F"We are also taking decisive action to
OL,7,Faddress veterans' concerns about
OL,8,Ffragmented support services through
OL,9,Four new #50m VALOUR programme. VALOUR
OL,10,Fwill improve veterans' access to
OL,11,Fessential care by enhancing
OL,12,Fcoordination at national, regional and
OL,13,Flocal levels, including field officers
OL,14,Facross the UK."
OL,16,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,17,FITVX
OL,19,FSign up for our free weekly newsletter
OL,20,Fhere.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/7
